Implemented the minimal source fix.

Changed:
- `crates/nu-protocol/src/process/child.rs`
  - Added a `check_exit_code` flag to `ChildProcess`.
  - `into_bytes()`/`wait()` now only turn non-zero exits into errors when that flag is enabled.
- `crates/nu-command/src/system/run_external.rs`
  - External commands whose stdout/stderr is piped to another command no longer enable exit-code error propagation.
- Updated direct `ChildProcess::new/from_raw` callers accordingly.

Verified:
- `cargo check -q -p nu-protocol -p nu-command -p nu-cmd-lang`
- `cargo fmt --check`
- Reproduced behavior:
  - external as final pipeline command still errors on exit code 1
  - external piped into `lines` does not error
  - external piped into `detect columns` no longer errors on exit code 1
